# Spinner Component Rule

The [Spinner.vue](mdc:src/components/ui/Spinner.vue) component follows shadcn-vue conventions:

- It is a single file component (SFC) in the `src/components/ui` directory.
- Used for displaying a spinning loading indicator.
- Uses Tailwind CSS for styling and utility classes.
- Accepts an optional `class` prop for custom styling.
- The spinner is a `div` with animated spin and border styles.

For loading indicator best practices, see the [shadcn-vue Skeleton documentation](mdc:https:/www.shadcn-vue.com/docs/components/skeleton) as a reference.





